726191f-a.title: Queens: Bowne Street - Roosevelt Avenue
726191f-a.text:
Bowne Street, north from Roosevelt Avenue. At the S. W. corner
of 38th Avenue is the First of Flushing Congregational Church.
P. L. Sperr  April 8, 1927
